title: BRIEF-Hengtong Optic-electric sees 9-mth profit up about 50-70 pct

BRIEF-Hengtong Optic-electric sees 9-mth profit up about 50-70 pct Sept 22 
Sept 22 Hengtong Optic-electric Co Ltd 
* Says expects Jan-Sept net profit up about 50-70 percent y/y at 373.9-423.7 million yuan ($58.66-66.47 million)
